message.56
	Congratulations! You've finished Savage Island successfully!\nRefer to instructions for following coded message:\nU L K # $ + S ( V A 0 3 5 D B I H\nO ; 7 E 8 / M P 4 J 1 T Q @ F % G\nW X 6 C ? Y , Z = & R * - N 2 ) 9
