	Captain's LOG:\nWounded in mutiny, strength failing. Humanoid seed colony not\nstarted, giant reptiles must be destroyed for species survival.
message.79
	TimeSwap Plan implemented with ROBOPIRATE as catalyst agent.\nIf you scanning this are not of THIS TIME then the mission\ncan still succeed!
